KnowledgeBase.Subtitle: Performing arts centre in the City of Sydney, New South Wales
KnowledgeBase.Description: The Sydney Opera House is a multi-venue performing arts centre at Sydney Harbour in Sydney, New South Wales, Australia. It is one of the 20th century's most famous and distinctive buildings. Wikipedia

Did you know: Paul Robeson was the first to perform in the Opera House.
